data.description:
Nestled in the charming locale of Wilton Manors, this exquisite two-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home invites you to experience the epitome of waterfront living.Step into a realm of modern sophistication as you explore the fully renovated interiors, adorned with impact glass that not only enhances the aesthetic appeal but also fills the living spaces with an abundance of natural daylight. The inclusion of skylights further elevates the ambiance, creating an atmosphere of warmth and openness. The outdoor oasis beckons with a heated saltwater pool, providing a perfect retreat for relaxation and entertainment. Revel in the pleasures of outdoor living with an impeccably designed kitchen, a convenient gas hookup, an invigorating outdoor shower, and a charming fire pit that sets the stage for unforgettable evenings.
The master bedroom serves as a private sanctuary, featuring a spa-inspired shower and an expansive walk-in closet that caters to both comfort and style. Immerse yourself in the luxury of this residence, where every detail has been carefully curated to offer a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality. Discover a lifestyle that embraces the serene beauty of waterfront living and the convenience of modern amenities, all within the heart of Wilton Manors.
